{"tid":277671,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"熱血鳳凰計劃搵笨柒","createTime":"2017-06-09T19:58:44.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-10T13:56:09.000Z","uid":4389,"like":2,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"fccbee8198124e6843c7bb8920a28866add57f56","tid":277671,"uid":4389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T19:58:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/10/031411_9aa638b030127a86f171055128b9327f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F10%2F031411_9aa638b030127a86f171055128b9327f.jpg&h=6138a23c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/10/031417_0e428a3b9d02282153b7538108b92a7f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F10%2F031417_0e428a3b9d02282153b7538108b92a7f.jpg&h=ed568a5f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n兩次講座收人$500，上次搞完壇野，相又無張，內容又無、得D空泛構思，點樣幫抗爭者重過新生？收得人5舊水，只係供應茶點，狼唔狼死阿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/10/032259_b8c84c38684bb1b40625e678d707ddba.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F10%2F032259_b8c84c38684bb1b40625e678d707ddba.jpg&h=38e920f4&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/10/032303_ba250409abce38ceea33f6513ed229eb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F10%2F032303_ba250409abce38ceea33f6513ed229eb.jpg&h=01bf4124&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n屌你老母臭閪，既然抗爭者係受港共政府逼害，當然要問政府拎錢搞社企幫助佢地更生。3百萬可以用3年，之後自負盈虧。<br />\n<br />\n不過首要條件係非牟利機構，熱血公民點樣cap到水阿，當然要用抗爭者名義，向你荷包打主意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"270c7837de0a54979c6a278ad5ecb772b7362293","tid":277671,"uid":47027,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T21:23:08.000Z","msg":"老千起個雞棚好辛苦架。"},{"pid":"82f552d4adaa5b4110a0f59f3c5df6bb3472202e","tid":277671,"uid":69568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T21:24:54.000Z","msg":"柏洋出返嚟嗱？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30f0eb56e118d8ae5f4864ddd9d7c2a376d34662","tid":277671,"uid":4389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T22:06:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>柏洋出返嚟嗱？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/10/060511_2ce348fc2ae530628d4aa50f3c420a58.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F10%2F060511_2ce348fc2ae530628d4aa50f3c420a58.jpg&h=48c8c481&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n出返黎加入老千行列<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，不過希望佢早日醒覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"240d7668e23d347295ec34c401ef627a42377dbb","tid":277671,"uid":90863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T22:14:10.000Z","msg":"非牟利機構已經fail"},{"pid":"f4aa849a9ef8feb4f7400e44e7503cba8f434660","tid":277671,"uid":4389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T22:16:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/10/061533_0f49a46c0f585ffd55857bae8f2cb4d0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F10%2F061533_0f49a46c0f585ffd55857bae8f2cb4d0.jpg&h=327a3533&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nSorry，原來連茶點都無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，得個爛鳩襟章<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbcb4e2c3f7e2435aef03f7f2f0a41592796303a","tid":277671,"uid":15224,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T22:18:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06